      <h2>MedicationPrescriptionStatus</h2>
		
      <p>A code specifying the state of the prescribing event. Describes the lifecycle of the prescription.</p>
		
      <p>This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/medication-prescription-status
		and omits the &quot;entered in error&quot; and &quot;superceded&quot; codes.</p>
		
      <table class="codes">
		  
        <tr>
			
          <td>
			  
            <b>Code</b>
			
          </td>
			
          <td>
			  
            <b>Definition</b>
			
          </td>
			
          <td>
			  
            <b>
				
              <a href="v3\ActStatus\index.html">v3 Map (ctStatus)</a>
			  
            </b>
			
          </td>
		  
        </tr>
		  
        <tr>
			
          <td>active
			  
            <a name="active"> </a>
			
          </td>
			
          <td>The prescription is &#39;actionable&#39;, but not all actions that are implied by it have occurred yet.</td>
			
          <td>
			  
            <span title=""/>
			  
            <a href="v3\ActStatus\index.html#active">active</a>
			
          </td>
		  
        </tr>
		  
        <tr>
			
          <td>on hold
			  
            <a name="onhold"> </a>
			
          </td>
			
          <td>Actions implied by the prescription have been temporarily halted, but are expected to continue later.  May also be called &quot;suspended&quot;.</td>
			
          <td>
			  
            <span title=""/>
			  
            <a href="v3\ActStatus\index.html#suspended">suspended</a>
			
          </td>
		  
        </tr>
		  
        <tr>
			
          <td>completed
			  
            <a name="completed"> </a>
			
          </td>
			
          <td>All actions that are implied by the prescription have occurred (this will rarely be made explicit).</td>
			
          <td>
			  
            <span title=""/>
			  
            <a href="v3\ActStatus\index.html#completed">completed</a>
			
          </td>
		  
        </tr>
		  
        <tr>
			
          <td>stopped
			  
            <a name="stopped"> </a>
			
          </td>
			
          <td>Actions implied by the prescription have been permanently halted, before all of them occurred.</td>
			
          <td>
			  
            <span title=""/>
			  
            <a href="v3\ActStatus\index.html#aborted">aborted</a>
			
          </td>
		  
        </tr>
		
      </table>
	  
